edu.brown.cs.wh7.Trie

Class TrieNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.wh7.Trie.TrieNode

  • public class TrieNode
extends Object
    Class that represnts a node in a Trie. Each Node only has one character and stores all of it's children in the tree.
    Author:
    wh7
